Package com.cognifide.qa.bb.logging.entries

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AssertionFailedEntry
    This entry represents a hard assertion that failed.
    BrowserInfoEntry
    This entry stores information about the browser.
    BrowserLogEntry
    Entry that represents an browser information that appeared during execution of the test.
    ErrorEntry
    Entry that represents an error that occurred during execution of the test.
    EventEntry
    This class represents a webDriver event.
    ExceptionEntry
    This class represents an exception that was caught during execution of the test.
    InfoEntry
    A simple info entry.
    LogEntry
    Base class for all types of log entries.
    LogEntryComparator  
    ScreenshotEntry
    Log entry with attached screenshot.
    SoftAssertionFailedEntry
    This entry class represents a soft assertion that failed.
    SubreportEndEntry
    This entry marks the end of a subreport
    SubreportStartEntry
    This entry marks the beginning of a subreport
